```plantuml
@startuml alextanhongpin_node-rest

[Express App] as App
[Config] as Config
[Database] as DB
[Helper] as Helper
[Schema] as Schema

package "Food Service" {
  [Route] as FoodRoute
  [Model] as FoodModel
  [Store] as FoodStore
}

App --> Config : uses
App --> DB : connects to
App --> Helper : uses
App --> Schema : validates with
App --> FoodRoute : routes requests to

FoodRoute --> FoodModel : delegates to
FoodModel --> FoodStore : uses
FoodModel --> Schema : validates with
FoodStore --> DB : interacts with

Config -[hidden]right-> DB
DB -[hidden]right-> Helper
Helper -[hidden]right-> Schema

@enduml
```